So that&#8217;s called being happy<br />
It makes you hope again<br />
That makes you happy, makes you happy, makes you happy</p>
<p>So that&#8217;s called being happy<br />
The feeling of not being alone<br />
So that&#8217;s called being happy<br />
To be together then</p>
